13
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:27,540
[Xi
Campus Heartthrob]

14
00:00:28,950 --> 00:00:32,110
You're so tempting.

15
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:36,450
What are you waiting for then?
Come and get me.

16
00:00:46,730 --> 00:00:50,610
Hey, who are you?
Hey, let me go!

17
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:54,330
Hey, let me go! Hey!

18
00:00:55,710 --> 00:00:56,940
